///
/// "Introduction"
@Node "intro" "Introduction"
@{b}Introduction@{ub}

GoScreen gives programs that have not an own screen a screen. Such as AmigaWriter, StormC and
DeluxeMusic 2.0. GoScreen is Shell only. A desired font can be choosen for the screen.

@{" How to use  " link "use"}

@EndNode
